description: Sicurezza per progetti Angular SSR/CSR e backend Node/Express. Provider-agnostico (Firebase, Vercel, AWS, Cloudflare, GCP). Universale.
globs: "**/*.ts, **/*.html, **/*.json, **/server.ts, **/*.yaml, **/*.yml, **/*.env*"
alwaysApply: true
